Text:
Thanks for the upload.

I love this show, but this has to be the worst ep ever.  The writers really dropped the ball on this one.

I'm NOT saying that you're wrong rc71, but this particular episode got a fairly normal rating (even slightly higher) on TV.com.

How's the video quality? Usually, when Orenji is the source - it's really poor.

Vid and audio qual is excellent.

Thanks for the info gregersamsa.  Too bad though.  Means they will make more ep like this one next year.
